<!-- INTRO DIALOGUE -->
  
  <!-- Fadein on Kitchen with PPGs and Professor -->
	<string id='intro_1'>Ah, what a nice relaxing day.</string>
	<string id='intro_2'>Don't get your hopes up, I have a feeling something is about to go down!</string>
	<string id='intro_3'>Nah, it'll be fine!</string>
	<string id='intro_4'>So, what would you girls like for dinner?</string>
	<!-- Gnat and mind controlled Bliss teleports in -->
	<string id='intro_5'>How about a nice big dish of revenge?</string>
	<string id='intro_6'>Bliss! What are you doing hanging around with this loser?</string>
	<string id='intro_7'>Well, this LOSER has complete control over Bliss...</string>
	<string id='intro_8'>What? How? Who are you again?</string>
	<string id='intro_9'>That's right! With my new mind control technology, me and Bliss will rule you all!</string>
	<string id='intro_10'>Oh and also my army of mutant bugs. Anyway, see ya! We have a lot to do!</string>
	<!-- Gnat and mind controlled Bliss teleport out -->
	<string id='intro_11'>We need to find them and help poor Bliss.</string>
	<string id='intro_12'>I'll send along some gadgets to help!</string>
	<string id='intro_13'>It looks like they were headed to Bird Poop Island! </string>
	<!-- Fadeout and start game -->
	
	
<!-- OUTRO DIALOGUE -->

	<!-- Fadein after defeating Bliss in final stage of boss battle -->
	<string id='outro_1'>You did it guys! You saved me from that loser!</string>
	<string id='outro_2'>I'm not a loser... sigh...</string>
	<string id='outro_3'>Of course we did!</string>
	<string id='outro_4'>We love you Bliss!</string>
	<string id='outro_5'>Let's go home and finally get some dinner</string>
	<string id='outro_6'>I'll be back! You'll see... ugh...</string>
	<!-- Fadeout --> 
	<string id='outro_7'>Thanks for Playing!</string>	
	<!-- Fadeout back to title card -->
	
	
